		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Frodo: Solo adventurer?</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='84' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/lotr/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='25'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(4.19)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=23733&PHPSESSID=88a61687069e6d57efa4fe386ae27e28">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=10894">Alex "Worlds" Weavers</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=10894&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Frodo is getting quite powerful these days - what, with Isildor&#39;s Bane giving him 5 vitality, Mithril making sure that he only takes one wound per skirmish, bounder making life tough for mulitiple enemies, plus the insane number of Hobbit boosties lyi</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> June 3, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Starting:<br />
<a href="javascript:card_browser(173)">Frodo, Old Bilbo&#39;s Heir</a><br />
<a href="javascript:card_browser(96)">The One Ring, Isildur&#39;s Bane</a><br />
<br />
Sites:<br />
